title: Honi Soit Qui Mal Y Pense
Shop 'Til You Drop
description: Sydney is representing a wealthy man who wants to divorce his wife but she insists on big payout which he refuses to grant. And in order to ensure she doesn't get anything, he starts giving his money away. Even buying gifts for everyone at Syd's office. And Charlie representing a guy is enamored by the lawyer of his client's wife who just happens to be his client's ex.

title: A Partridge in a Pair's Tree
